{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Abolish Mobile Roaming Charges for UK Travellers to Europe",
        "additional_details": "UK mobile users now face what we believe to be excessive and hidden fees when travelling abroad. We think that banning roaming charges will make travelling to the continent a far easier experience.\r\n \r\nThe Government should introduce legislation to require mobile telephone service providers to continue allowing EU wide roaming at no extra charge, similar to the situation before Brexit.\r\n",
        "background": "Since the UK's departure from the European Union, many mobile phone users have been subject to roaming charges when travelling to the continent.",
